<li>Open the helicopter body.</li>
<li>Remove the wires and take out the board and battery</li>
<br /><br />
</ol>

<h2 id="step-8-connect-the-board-to-the-drone-frame">Step 8: Connect the Board to the Drone Frame.</h2>
<p>
<img style="border-radius: 3px" width="230px" height="230px" src="https://content.instructables.com/ORIG/FNO/6U1R/J7MF2JOC/FNO6U1RJ7MF2JOC.jpg?auto=webp&amp;frame=1&amp;width=800&amp;height=1024&amp;fit=bounds&amp;md=2bad4815fa08a1e9ce385270ff27564f" />
                                    
